text:
There are about 20 basic-look Black and White Bungalows at Eng Neo Avenue, a place known for GCBA (Good Class Bungalow Area).
Presently, these state properties are under the care of SLA (Singapore Land Authority).
Eng Neo Avenue is named after Tan Eng Neo aka Tan Eng Nio, wife of Gaw Boon Chan, founder of Ho Ho Biscuilt Factory.
